  Tu2-gu7 Siu2-jin5 chhut-khi3, au7-lai5 chiah chai si7 khi3 sun5 chhan5-chui2, giah8 chit8 ki ti5-thau5 tui3 hng7-hng7 teh lai5, tai7-khai3 si7 siuN7 kong2 chhan5-chui2 long2 sun5-liau2 beh koah tiu7-a2 e5 si5 chit8 e5 lang5 choe3 chit8 pian3 eng7 chhiam-taN taN tit 4 taN3 chhek. Si3-pah goa7 kin, oa2 500 kin lat8. Kui2 e5 lang5-a2 oa2 lai5 i bo5 lun2--tioh8, koh u7 oh8 kun5-thau5, kha-chhiu2 chin ho2. Goeh8 hou7 hun5 kham3-leh, goeh8-kng hoan2-ou hoan2-ou. KhoaN3 thau5-cheng5 chit8-tin7 lang5 kng chit8-teng2 kio7, kng-teh-chhek8, poaN3-kau2-chau2. In m7-kaN2 kng tui3 toa7-be2-lou7, si7 chau2 tui3 sio2-lou7-a2, chiah e7 hiah tu2-ho2 kap Siu2-jin5 sio cheng-thau5. Siu2-jin5 ia7 put-kai2 ki5-i3 ian5-lou7 gim5-si choe3 phoaN7 bo5-lam7-bo5-lam7 kin2 gim5 kin2-kiaN5. Kio7-lai7 Hui7-bi2 jin7-tit si7 Siu2-jin5 e5 siaN am3-am3 hoaN-hi2, ki5-to2 Chu2 pang-chan7, ng3-bang7 u7 kiu3. Tiam7-tiam7 m7-kaN2 chhut-siaN. ThiaN gim5-si e5 siaN na2-kin7, chiu7 chai Siu2-jin5 i2-keng oa2 lai5 kau3 sin-piN, hut-jian5 tui3 kio7-lai7 toa7-siaN kio3, ¡§Siu2-jin5 kin2 lai5 kiu3 goa2.¡¨ Siu2-jin5 jin7-tit si7 Hui7-bi2 e5 siaN koh khoaN3 su7-koaN choe3 cheng5 kiaN5, chit8 pou7 hun7 e5 lang5 i2-keng chau2 chin3-cheng5. In-ui7 Hui7-bi2 chin gau5, Siong7-te3 hou7 i u7 ti3-sek, tui3 thiaN Siu2-jin5 gim5-si e5 siaN hit-si5, i ti7 kio7-lai7 thiau-ti5 ngiauh8-ngiauh8-tang7, kio7 io5-lai5, io5-khi3, u7 si5 giong7-giong7 beh peng2-kio7, kng kio7 e5 si7 ka-teng koh m7-si7 kio7-hu, bo5 koan3-si3, kio3-khou2 lian5-thian. Sou2-i2 su7-koaN kap chit8 pou7-hun7 e5 peng long2 chau2 chin3-cheng5 khi3. Chhun chit8 pou7-hun7 ka-teng kou3 kio7 chau2 ban7 sui5 ti7 kio7-au7. Siu2-jin5 thiaN Hui7-bi2 sio2-chia2 teh kio3 i, chek-si5 kam2-kak si7 pang2-hui2 liah8 lang5, i si7 m7-chai Khun-hong kap in bo2-ku7 teh piN3-kui2. Siu2-jin5 e5 tit8-kam2 si7 pang2-hui2 liah8 lang5 beh kong3 hoan-thau5. Che ia7-si7 TiuN chiong-kun cha2 choe3 lek8-lim5 pang2-siu2 e5 ku7-thng-thau5. Siu2-jin5 chek-si5 chau2-oa2 siong3 cheng-cheng